This paper discusses the use of blockchain technology to secure and attribute incoming data streams from sensors for open science projects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
